Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能帮他们  但缉毒局有太多繁文缛节\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I could help them, but the DEA has so much red tape.
