Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  追踪你不会花太久的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, won't take long to retrace your steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说我现在该做笔交易吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Saying I should make a deal now?
