Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你之前已经逮捕一个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you've already arrested one of them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I did,
