Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些比你大不了多少的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}kids not much older than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替他们蹲监狱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to get them out of prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都有自己的立场  我为什么要相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Look, everybody got an angle, why should I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我身处你和他们之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}'Cause I'm the one standing between you and them.
