Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想当男子汉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You wanna be the man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先照顾好你的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Start taking care of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什么不测\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Anything happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你照顾好小特\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You take care of T.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I give you my word.
