Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:22:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我们买衣服花掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Except for what we spent on clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信缉毒局能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sure the DEA will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支援随时会来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Back up will be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带你妹妹去一下卫生间  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get your sister and make sure she uses the bathroom, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子很聪明  汤姆森会来接的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kid's smart. Thomsen'll pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先确保冲出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need to make it out of here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll do a sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I should go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防兄弟会的人等着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In case the Brotherhood's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你担心我吗  警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You worried about me, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没你帮助  我也走到了今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I made it this far without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  迷你  坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, Mini, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己拷到管子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Cuff yourself to the pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.27,0:24:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得看情况了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我想知道的事  就是休息区\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You tell me what I want to know, it's a pit-stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的安息区\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}it's your final resting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now where's Dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎样  小姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What you gonna do, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打我一顿拷问我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You gonna beat it out of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.05,0:24:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Isn't that what you would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.38,0:24:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必多问\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why bother asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.72,0:24:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我  我们不是一类人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You and me, we ain't even close to the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.16,0:24:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.64,0:24:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种预感你能忍受疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got a hunch you can take the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至乐在其中  就像我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You might even enjoy it. Like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.65,0:24:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们要做朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So now we gonna be friends?
