Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克怎么没派人来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}so how come Dominic hasn't sent anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.14,0:24:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许因为他知道我自己能解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe 'cause he knows I can handle my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.63,0:24:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你只是不值得让他们找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or maybe you're just not worth the gas it takes to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.28,0:24:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在休克的第一阶段\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're in the first stages of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.61,0:25:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出汗  细脉  失去血色\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sweaty, thready pulse, loss of color.
