Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.64,0:25:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么告诉我多米尼克在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or you can just tell me where Dominic is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是说了  你觉得我会怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If I tell you, what do you think will happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.87,0:25:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是死在另一个地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just end up in another basement.
