Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.53,0:25:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就放你出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I will get you out of dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.80,0:25:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧  迷你  放聪明点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Come on, Mini, be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏玩久一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Play the long game.
