Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.37,0:25:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.56,0:25:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他妈怎么做都一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Doesn't make a damn bit of a difference what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.93,0:25:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥做都一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or who you do it for.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dominic ain't no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.94,0:25:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他人没区别\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just another man like all the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.60,0:25:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克似乎要比你说得聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sounds like this Dominic's a lot smarter than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.37,0:25:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多几年  他就会下台\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Couple years on top, he'll burn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.39,0:25:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者送命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or get wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.90,0:25:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一条真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Only one rule:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.57,0:25:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最终都难逃一死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We all die in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.15,0:25:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伦诺克斯特工已经走好一会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Agent Lennox's been gone awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.25,0:26:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是不是遇到麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Think she ran into trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.19,0:26:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人之前肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got a feeling that woman's stared trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.95,0:26:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历过不少风浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in the face more than a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.76,0:26:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sure she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.89,0:26:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  莱奈尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's up, Lionel?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.78,0:26:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以请  我吃牛排来谢我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, you can--uh--thank me with a prime rib,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.26,0:26:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者双烤土豆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe some twice-baked potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.48,0:26:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在点餐呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You placing a dinner order,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.95,0:26:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是有什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or is there a reason for your call?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.28,0:26:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你硬塞给我的那桩七杀案\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know that septuple homicide you saddled me with?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.64,0:26:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在一部手机上发现条线索\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got a lead off one of the cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个电话号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A number.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.87,0:26:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟会的人在凶案现场打了这个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Brotherhood banger called it from the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.24,0:26:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.03,0:26:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你不想和多米尼克对话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So didn't you want to have a chat with Dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.84,0:26:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能是他的号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This could be his number.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.41,0:26:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你只有一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you'll only get to call it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.27,0:26:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就打打看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Better make that call then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.29,0:26:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会有这个手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where'd you get that phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.98,0:26:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伦诺克斯特工给我的  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Agent Lennox gave it to me, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.38,0:26:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  搭档\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is there a problem, partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.25,0:26:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来缉毒缉局的确有兄弟会内鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Seems the DEA does have a mole working for the brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.92,0:26:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伦诺克斯特工骗了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Agent Lennox double-crossed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.99,0:26:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还保证呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Gave me your word huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.74,0:26:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说是没有支援了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So we don't have back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.21,0:26:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有支援  只不过要久一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We do, it's just gonna take a little longer than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.96,0:27:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑住  我马上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sit tight. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.77,0:27:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You'd better make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.75,0:27:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被包围了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.52,0:27:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有缉毒局内线的最新情况吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have you heard from our snitch in the DEA, lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.84,0:27:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  不过她说警察和孩子就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, but she said the cop and the kid are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.15,0:27:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上嘴  就饶你一命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Keep your mouth shut and you'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.87,0:27:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  弗斯科预计多久到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Finch, you got an ETA on Fusco?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.87,0:27:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八分钟  视交通状况而定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Eight minutes based on current traffic patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.45,0:27:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能把兄弟会拖到那时么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can you hold off the Brotherhood until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.42,0:27:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正有此意\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.65,0:27:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想伦诺克斯女士拿到毒品钱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I imagine Ms. Lennox has recovered the drug money by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.44,0:27:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她是内鬼  兄弟会为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But if she's their mole, then why is the Brotherhood
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.31,0:27:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在追杀孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}still after the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.55,0:27:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能她不止骗了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps we're not the only ones she's double-crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.48,0:27:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她留下了手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Would explain why she left her cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.52,0:27:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟会就追踪不到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So the Brotherhood can't trace her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.19,0:27:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸  我们也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nor can we, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.91,0:27:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十万足够让人失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}$1/2 million is more than enough to disappear for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.78,0:27:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就没这么幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're not so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.07,0:28:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟会拿不到钱不会罢手的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Brotherhood's not backing down without their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.59,0:28:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退而求其次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What about the next best thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.46,0:28:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖女士  你有多米尼克的位置了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ms. Shaw, have you located dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.16,0:28:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.64,0:28:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我和大块头谈了谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I had a chat with our big friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.74,0:28:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留他一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}left him alone to cool off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.42,0:28:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那些冒火的同伙没来找他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That guy's angry his boys ain't come looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.32,0:28:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来救名打手不是他们的首要任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guess saving a piece of muscle's not high on their priority list.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.18,0:28:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们该重新考虑下任务的重要性了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They should rethink their priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.99,0:28:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大块头气得想干架\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Muscle's gonna be looking for a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.89,0:28:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他会去找多米尼克算账\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you think he'll confront dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.76,0:28:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他已经火冒三丈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think he's just mad enough to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.79,0:28:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大块头是条小鱼  但他能引出大鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Our guy's a little fish, but he could lead us to the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.64,0:28:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把小鱼放回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So throw the minnow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You two ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.58,0:28:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要冲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.19,0:28:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改主意了  我不想走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I changed my mind. I don't wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.77,0:28:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾西  水枪还在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tracie, do you still have your squirt gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.01,0:28:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.39,0:28:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以备用\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Could come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.31,0:28:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要玩躲猫猫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}'cause we're gonna play hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.51,0:28:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.46,0:28:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这游戏我擅长\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm really good at this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.17,0:29:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子躲在楼顶房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kids are holed up in the penthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.40,0:29:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关掉摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kill the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.95,0:29:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What the--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.23,0:29:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边  他们正往上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This way. They're coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.96,0:29:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.21,0:29:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察在我妈那里搜到的枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That gun the cops found on my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.32,0:29:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.67,0:30:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈撒了谎  说枪是她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My mom lied. She said it belonged to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.48,0:30:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是我  她根本不会蹲监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She wouldn't even be in jail if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.35,0:30:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要枪做什么  马尔科姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why'd you have a gun, Malcolm?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.05,0:30:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了自保\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just wanted to protect my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.45,0:30:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却弄巧成拙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All I did was make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.41,0:30:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.63,0:30:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.22,0:30:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并非不能改正\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Doesn't mean you can't make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.02,0:30:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.41,0:30:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱早没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Money's long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先逃出去  再来担心下边的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's get out of here and we'll worry about the rest later.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.08,0:30:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Go, go, go.
