Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.93,0:32:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带你妹妹躲起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Take your sister and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.20,0:32:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Go.
