Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.76,0:32:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做个交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I wanna make a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.54,0:33:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命换我妹妹的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My life for my sister's.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.59,0:33:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说重点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Best be getting to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.96,0:33:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的钱呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's my money?
