Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.74,0:33:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.27,0:33:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你告过别了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I hope you said your good-byes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.45,0:33:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你忘了什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think you're forgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.30,0:34:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要钱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you want your money?
