Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.19,0:34:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用错误去纠正错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You can't make something right by doing something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.48,0:34:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.51,0:34:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  照顾好你妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Go, you take care of your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.59,0:34:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说完了  警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You done, Detective?
