Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.75,0:36:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天还是我的好日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Like I said, it's my lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.47,0:36:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Excuse me.
