Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.73,0:37:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以放警探走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Say I let the detective go...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.17,0:37:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你凭什么保证你就不会动手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}how do I know you're gonna back off?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.85,0:37:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你留份分手礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll leave you a parting gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.44,0:37:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷你陪着你的毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mini here can keep your drugs company.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.09,0:37:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今天不是你的好日子啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guess it's not your lucky day after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.01,0:38:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没说你为谁干活儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Never said who you worked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.96,0:38:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我没说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're right. I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.28,0:38:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你老大  回见\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tell your boss I'll be seeing him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.13,0:38:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上学真的没问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You sure you're okay to go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.33,0:38:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了  你没事  我就没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Told you. I'm okay if you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我  我们要永远在一起  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You and me. We stick together, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.82,0:38:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  明天见\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.55,0:38:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.98,0:38:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以后每天都能见到特蕾西了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Actually, you'll be seeing Tracie later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.49,0:38:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你的社工谈了谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I had a little chat with you social worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.29,0:38:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你就会被接到一个新家  你们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've been assigned a new home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.47,0:38:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.77,0:38:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你死了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}For a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.28,0:38:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林克怎么会放你走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How'd you get Link to let you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.66,0:38:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很有说服力啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Turns out I can be pretty persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.07,0:38:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.96,0:38:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你联系了一名律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got you a consultation with a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.81,0:39:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高手  哈佛毕业的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dream team. Harvard law.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.37,0:39:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}莱丝丽·奎尔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.41,0:39:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多材料可以给她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got a few articles I could send her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.07,0:39:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱恩杰·罗姆一案  还有布莱恩·艾肯一案\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The people versus Ryan Jerome, or the Brian D. Aitken's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.07,0:39:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}前者为强奸  后者为抚养权案
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.02,0:39:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  马尔科姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know what, Malcolm?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.76,0:39:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你一定能成为一个好律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think you'd make a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.11,0:39:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想当警察呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was thinking about being a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.85,0:39:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.80,0:39:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你  不过我会少突突人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Like you, but I'd shoot less people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.52,0:39:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当男子汉  得有计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wanna be the man, gotta have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.85,0:39:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情提醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As a friendly reminder,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.90,0:39:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请乘客们站在黄色安全线后候车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}all passengers, please stand beind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.79,0:39:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有人坐吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This seat taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.63,0:39:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个自由的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's a free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.53,0:39:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起码曾经是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}At least it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.80,0:39:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有心事吗  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something troubling you, Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.92,0:39:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次见面时  你问了我个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The last time we met, you asked me a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.34,0:39:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你撒谎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.39,0:40:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕真相会陷你于致命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm afraid the truth would put you in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你这么关心我  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I didn't know you cared, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.83,0:40:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常有致命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've been in danger before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.25,0:40:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这次完全不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, this is something altogether different.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.17,0:40:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能说  你说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All I can say is, you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.41,0:40:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界已经改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.40,0:40:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是回不去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I suppose there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.34,0:40:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我来找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Which brings me to the reason I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.21,0:40:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}《隐身人》  赫·乔·威尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.65,0:40:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗示吗  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A hint, Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.37,0:40:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多事之秋的一点建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Advice for these troubled times.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.26,0:40:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点答谢礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And a little thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.07,0:40:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}纽约市阿斯托利亚36号大街  33-191
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.68,0:40:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟会的藏货地址  至少五小时前是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's the location of the Brotherhood's stash house as of five hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.31,0:40:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒品这会儿肯定转移了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No doubt, the drugs have been relocated by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.78,0:40:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我知道你热衷于调查对手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I know how dedicated you are to studying your adversaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.21,0:40:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你想知道我是否知道了多米尼克的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I suppose you'll want to know if I identify this Dominic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.20,0:40:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.02,0:41:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时局变幻莫测啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's a tricky business.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.69,0:41:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场游戏要在一团迷雾中玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Playing a game in which you're unsure of the pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.84,0:41:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这场游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And in this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.95,0:41:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕根本输不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I fear that losing is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.94,0:41:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠  你是猫吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Damn, you like a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.99,0:41:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少九条命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You got at least nine lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.73,0:41:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏货应该是没保住吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was worried we gonna lose the stash though.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.22,0:41:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洛因很安全  起码现在是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"H" is safe. For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.73,0:41:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那贱人逼你说出地址了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Bitch made you tell her the location?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.31,0:41:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小妞一直跟踪我  甩不掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Chick was tracking me. I couldn't shake her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.06,0:41:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能给她点真料  她才肯罢休\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I had to lead her to something of value so she'd back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.53,0:41:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想派人去救你  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I would have sent somebody for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.23,0:41:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你只能听命行事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you were just following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.98,0:41:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他的叛徒也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I wish his rat would have did the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.96,0:42:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她偷货时候被我抓个正着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I caught this chick stealing crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.42,0:42:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.15,0:42:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们老大呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's your boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.56,0:42:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚见到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You just met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.38,0:42:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}Every day I see you looking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.48,0:42:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们总是低估你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They always underestimate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.02,0:42:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布克那孩子也偷了我们的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Booker kids stole from us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.55,0:42:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子倒是挺有头脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Little man's got a good head on his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.59,0:42:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适合给我们干活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kind of kid should be working for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.19,0:42:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做通他母亲的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Spring his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.34,0:42:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他知道谁才是背后老大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Make sure he knows who pulled the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.50,0:42:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子会回来投奔我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Boy'll find his way back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.67,0:42:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全心全意归顺\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hearts and minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.47,0:42:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个警察莱利呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What about that cop, Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.11,0:42:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那贱人跟他一伙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And that bitch that was helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.69,0:42:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂他们到底在玩哪一套\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Still trying to figure out what game they playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.59,0:42:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是毫无章法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Seems like they not playing by no rule book.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.38,0:42:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那警察很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Cop's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.55,0:42:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟我们没什么不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But he's no different than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.19,0:42:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察永远都有  黑帮也永不消亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There'll always be cops, like there'll always be gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.38,0:43:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一条真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Only one rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.51,0:43:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  多米尼克\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's that, Dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.95,0:43:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最终都难逃一死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We all die in the end.
